c=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n按DSE講法, elastic collision係KE conserve only,淨係KE<br />\n<br />\n所以條題目變左KE_a +KE_b = KE_a&rsquo; + KE_b&rsquo;<br />\na係orbital果粒, b係撞入去果粒，當有2E咁，佢assume撞完，果2E比曬electron A變佢既KE加PE，自己KE 0撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，咁2E拆左d去PE,咁就唔conserve，KE_a + KE_b 唔等於 KE_a' 就inelastic <br />\n<br />\n但大學level黎講，成件事就好奇怪，你睇到上面就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nphoton同electron叫唔叫collision呢,其實會叫scattering，有個effect叫compton effect，講d野差不多，咁佢都係define做scattering而唔係collision,咁連collision都稱不上咁A自然唔理喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過你dse就是但喇當乜都係collision<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64cda4e6ece850e21213cd3ee7e48d444c091d1a","tid":2202702,"uid":86196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65e04c9e12db7a5db1949b1b33966bf417b3d5a3","tid":2202702,"uid":86196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T12:31:02.000Z","msg":"總結番上面既人講既野，廢時搞到d dse雞好亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n按DSE講法, elastic collision係KE conserve only,淨係KE<br />\n<br />\n所以條題目變左KE_a +KE_b = KE_a&rsquo; + KE_b&rsquo;<br />\na係orbital果粒, b係撞入去果粒，當有2E咁，佢assume撞完，果2E比曬electron A變佢既KE加PE，自己KE 0撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，咁2E拆左d去PE,咁就唔conserve，KE_a + KE_b 唔等於 KE_a' 就inelastic <br />\n<br />\n但大學level黎講，成件事就好奇怪，你睇到上面就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nphoton同electron叫唔叫collision呢,其實會叫scattering，有個effect叫compton effect，講d野差不多，咁佢都係define做scattering而唔係collision,咁連collision都稱不上咁A自然唔理喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過你dse就是但喇當乜都係collision<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T12:34:28.000Z","msg":"overall黎講cw shum唔係好解釋for dse<i